  "name": "Sekhmet Terminator Cabal",
  "titles": "Sekhmet Terminator Cabal",
  "lore": "The Sekhmet were the elite of the Thousand Sons, and when called upon, served as Magnus’ bodyguard. Clad in Terminator armour, each was a high initiate of the Prosperine Mysteries who had sublimated their abilities and emotions into the highest levels of control. Marked by the jade scarab bonded to their armour, they stood apart from others of the Legion, a brotherhood within a brotherhood. Able to hold their minds at the highest levels of the Enumerations, the Scarab Occult fought with such unified precision and control that they seemed to some less warriors of flesh and blood but more automata sculpted in the form of men.",
